name: Wickiup Canyon
description:
Introduction

Descent

Pants and long sleeves recommended. Be mindful of loose rock in and around the drainage.

Numerous downclimbs, a few of which are moderately challenging. The two rappels are under 100 ft and both anchored from pinch points.

Background

First descended by Garrett Bennett and Bill Shoemaker in the Fall of 2010.
